Here we go!

RepoMaker 2.0... or at least 1.9.3 

Some of the new improvements are: 
Update notifications... so if you getting an update note, please use 

repo -dev 

to update to the latest version ;)


HOWTO:

Download all Files.
open terminal

"sudo cp repo /usr/bin/repo"

"mkdir /RepoMaker"

"cp sample_repo.conf /RepoMaker/sample_repo.conf"

Open the conf file in your Fav text editor and Change the Settings as u like.

Rename it to repo.conf

and your ready to go :)